{"type":"text","timestamp":1775860439126,"sessionID":"ses_2867ff01bffe0zLX0iGGpKvf3Z","part":{"id":"prt_d7987b45d001w0x2BOnHgShP8Q","messageID":"msg_d7987ab74001o8UDeScUqsXcmE","sessionID":"ses_2867ff01bffe0zLX0iGGpKvf3Z","type":"text","text":"**AR-025 Implementation Complete.**\n\nSummary of changes:\n\n**`agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`:**\n- Added verbose logging to `load_metadata()`, `save_metadata()`, and `update_metadata()` per spec\n- Enhanced `validate_workspace()` to check directory existence and type (per delta-spec)\n- Fixed `update_metadata()` to properly validate updates via `AgentMetadata(**data)` reconstruction (Pydantic v2's `model_copy` doesn't re-run validators)\n\n**`agentcube/models/pack_models.py`:**\n- No changes needed — already matches spec exactly\n\n**`tests/services/test_metadata_model.py`:**\n- Added `TestAgentMetadataRequiredFields` (missing `agent_name`, missing `entrypoint`)\n- Added `TestAgentMetadataOptionalDefaults` (all optional fields default to `None`)\n\n**`tests/services/test_metadata_service.py`:**\n- Added `TestLoadMetadataInvalidYaml` (malformed YAML raises `yaml.YAMLError`)\n- Added `TestLoadMetadataValidationFailure` (unsupported language raises `ValidationError`)\n- Added `TestLoadMetadataVerbose` (verbose logging on load)\n- Added `TestSaveMetadataVerbose` (verbose logging on save)\n- Added `TestUpdateMetadataInvalidValues` (invalid port raises `ValidationError`)\n- Added `TestUpdateMetadataVerbose` (verbose logging on update)\n- Added `TestValidateWorkspace` (valid dir, missing dir, file not dir, empty workspace)\n- Added `TestValidatePythonWorkspace` (py files present, multiple files, no files raises, missing requirements raises)\n- Added `TestValidateJavaWorkspace` (pom.xml present, pom.xml missing raises)\n- Fixed `workspace_with_primary` fixture to include `requirements.txt`\n- Fixed `TestSaveMetadataFormat` to use nested dict for indentation check\n\n**Results:** 51/51 tests pass, ruff clean.","time":{"start":1775860439122,"end":1775860439122}}}
